entry.title: Winter Weather Advisory issued November 19 at 10:12AM CST until November 20 at 12:00AM CST by NWS
entry.summary: ...SNOW EXPECTED TO CREATE HAZARDOUS TRAVEL CONDITIONS IN THE LAKE SUPERIOR SNOWBELT THROUGH THIS EVENING... .Prevailing northwest winds will bring lake-effect snow showers from Lake Superior into the area this afternoon and this evening. The snow showers will taper off late tonight as winds turn to a more westerly direction.
